description: This luxury two plus bedroom, two and a half bath at the St. Regis building is the epitome of sophisticated city living! The unit features endless views with large floor to ceiling windows that offer an abundance of natural light and a stunning backdrop for your daily life. The interior is elegantly appointed with high-end finishes and state-of-the-art appliances, creating a comfortable and stylish living space. The open-concept living and dining area is perfect for entertaining guests or relax on the private balcony and enjoy the scenery after a long day. The gourmet kitchen features sleek cabinetry, granite countertops, and top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances, making it a joy to cook in. The bedrooms are spacious and the primary bath features radiant heat floors and walk-in shower. The additional space is a perfect at home office or den. The building offers its residents a range of exceptional amenities, including 24-hour concierge, fitness center, and an indoor swimming pool.
